    {
      "id": "6wqCcKEkl2V8YUCnyUV7Y",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3183.0675659179688,
      "y": 257.8589324951172,
      "width": 851.41943359375,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 957933657,
      "version": 381,
      "versionNonce": 410447065,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781602806979,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How to generate short URL\n\n1. use hashing algo like MD5 ( size will be high)\n2. use base62 encoding ( a-z, A-Z and 0-9)\n\noption 2 preferred\n\nwe get long url -> create numeric ID -> convert number to base62 encoding and persist\n\nhow to generate ID?\nuse snowflake approach\n\n62 bits\n50 bits timestamp\ndatacenter id + machineid 10 bits\n12 bits sequence id\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How to generate short URL\n\n1. use hashing algo like MD5 ( size will be high)\n2. use base62 encoding ( a-z, A-Z and 0-9)\n\noption 2 preferred\n\nwe get long url -> create numeric ID -> convert number to base62 encoding and persist\n\nhow to generate ID?\nuse snowflake approach\n\n62 bits\n50 bits timestamp\ndatacenter id + machineid 10 bits\n12 bits sequence id\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
